## Communication Protocol

### When Tests Fail
1. **STOP** - Do not commit code
2. **ANALYZE** - Identify root cause
3. **FIX** - Address the issue
4. **RE-RUN** - Validate fix with full test suite
5. **DOCUMENT** - Record issue & resolution

### Telegram Reporting
- Send automated reports after test runs
- Include pass rates, failures, duration
- Tag responsible developers
- Link to test artifacts/logs
- Escalate critical failures immediately

